## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the complexity of economic factors influencing money velocity. The analysis primarily relies on secondary sources, which may not capture all nuances of the issue. Additionally, the dynamic nature of economic conditions means that the factors affecting money velocity can change rapidly, necessitating ongoing research and analysis.

